description:
ParameterChangeRequests:  A table recording requests to change parameters in a radio access network, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, request IDs, data type, format version, and details of the change requests.

dateTime: Timestamp of the parameter change request.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the affected cell(s).
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell where the parameter change is requested.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  An additional identifier (likely redundant in this sample data).
vsDataType:  Type of data in the request (e.g., parameter change request).
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format used in the request.
ParameterChangeRequests.parameterChangeRequestsId: Unique identifier for the parameter change request.
ParameterChangeRequests.parameterChangeRequestList:  Detailed list of parameter changes requested (currently empty in sample).
ParameterChangeRequests.latestUpdate: Timestamp of the latest update to the request (currently empty in sample).
